      <p>Our site may use cookies or similar technologies to enhance user experience. These are used for site functionality and analytics only.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Your Choices</h2>
      <p>You may contact us to update or remove your information. We will respond according to applicable privacy obligations.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, please reach out to AgriLinkHub at Minakulu Trading Centre A, Oyam District, Northern Uganda, Uganda.</p>
    </section>
